Le Havre vs Lens - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 17
description: Le Havre have only lost 10% of their home games against Lens in the 21st century in all competitions, having a lower percentage against no other team they’ve faced at least 10 times at their stadium. HAC are on a nine-match unbeaten run at home against RCL in all competitions, their last loss coming in May 2003, also in Ligue 1. Defeated for the 12th time in Ligue 1 in 2024/25 on Sunday in Marseille, Le Havre are the fourth team in the 21st century to have at least 12 losses after 16 games in a L1 season after Grenoble in 2009/10, Metz in 2017/18 and Angers in 2022/23. All three teams were relegated at the end of the season.

title: Nantes vs Monaco - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 17

Mathis Abline is the author of 24% of Nantes’ shots in Ligue 1 2024/25, with only Mason Greenwood posting a higher percentage for his team this season.

title: PSG vs Saint-Étienne - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 17

title: DTM Show 2025-Zandvoort
description: DTM. The embodiment of Motorsport tradition. Having just turned 40, the DTM combines a unique fascination and familiarity with an unmistakable dynamic, signified by the rebranding with a new logo! And with the addition of Ford, the palette of different brands is only increasing!
